casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Maiorano.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Maiorano (1987), 31 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(D.R. No. 87-5 Decided July 15, 1987.)

The resignation of Alexander Maiorano as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
